thread.title: TV | Strictly Come Dancing

author: entertainment.ie
title: TV | Strictly Come Dancing
text: If you're in need of a campy, glitzy break after all the rugby on Saturday, you can't get more campy and glitzy than Strictly. The fifteen celebs and their dance partners, including Peter Andre and our own wee Daniel, will take to the dancefloor for the second time to hop, skip, jive and more in an effort to save themselves from the first elimination. Who goes? You Britain unfortunately decides. But we're sure Daniel will do fine, his fans are a dab hand at keeping him going sure.
